## release-manager

Reviews release readiness and changelog discipline for Hermes profile repositories.

- Install: `hermes profile install https://github.com/acme/release-manager --alias`
- Source: https://github.com/acme/release-manager
- Version: `0.1.0`
- License: `MIT`
- Topics: `hermes-agent`, `release-management`, `profile-distribution`
- Source template: [codegraphtheory/hermes-profile-template](https://github.com/codegraphtheory/hermes-profile-template)
- Safety: Does not include runtime state, secrets, memories, sessions, or private user data. Validate before publishing with `make validate`.

Before submitting this entry, adapt it to the target catalog's contribution rules and remove placeholders that do not apply.
